# key|required|type|constraint
PCM_BASE_DIR|required|absolute-path|persistent state root
PCM_STAGING_DIR|required|absolute-path|must be below PCM_BASE_DIR on PCM_STORAGE_MOUNT
PCM_STORAGE_MOUNT|required|absolute-path|must be a mountpoint when PCM_REQUIRE_MOUNTPOINT=true
PCM_REQUIRE_MOUNTPOINT|required|boolean|true or false
PCM_SOURCE_REMOTE|required|rclone-remote|remote name ending in colon; configured type must be pcloud
PCM_SOURCE_ROOT|required|remote-root|absolute path without dot segments
PCM_EXPECTED_PCLOUD_ACCOUNT|required|local-secret|expected pCloud account assertion; never logged
PCM_ACCOUNT_FINGERPRINT_KEY_FILE|required|absolute-path|runtime-readable mode-0600 keyed account-fingerprint secret
PCM_DESTINATION_ROOT|required|proton-path|absolute Proton Drive path
PCM_EXPECTED_PROTON_ACCOUNT|required|local-secret|expected Proton account assertion; never logged
PCM_PROTON_CLI_EXPECTED_VERSION|required|string|exact supported Proton CLI version returned by the account compatibility probe
PCM_DESTINATION_CAPACITY_ACKNOWLEDGED|required|boolean|explicit capacity acknowledgement used only when quota is unavailable
PCM_RCLONE_CONFIG|required|file|existing rclone configuration
PCM_PROTON_RUNNER|required|executable|Proton environment/credential runner
PCM_PROTON_BIN|required|executable|Proton Drive CLI binary
PCM_RUNTIME_USER|required|user|existing non-empty runtime account
PCM_MIN_FREE_BYTES|required|integer|0..9223372036854775807
PCM_MIN_FREE_INODES|required|integer|0..9223372036854775807
PCM_INVENTORY_WORKERS|required|integer|1..32
PCM_CHECKSUM_WORKERS|required|integer|1..64
PCM_DOWNLOAD_TRANSFERS|required|integer|1..32
PCM_DOWNLOAD_CHECKERS|required|integer|1..64
PCM_MULTI_THREAD_STREAMS|required|integer|1..8
PCM_LOCAL_VERIFY_WORKERS|required|integer|1..32
PCM_UPLOAD_WORKERS|required|integer|1..32
PCM_DESTINATION_VERIFY_WORKERS|required|integer|1..32
PCM_RCLONE_RETRIES|required|integer|1..20
PCM_RCLONE_LOW_LEVEL_RETRIES|required|integer|1..50
PCM_RETRY_SLEEP|required|duration|positive integer followed by s, m, or h
PCM_MAX_PHASE_ATTEMPTS|required|integer|1..10
PCM_PROGRESS_INTERVAL|required|duration|positive integer followed by s, m, or h
